item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Dns_Domain_Registration_List
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Dns_Domain_Registration_List Datatype Description Local domainName The domain name. Type: string encodingType Three-character language tag for the IDN domain that you're trying to register. This is only required for IDN domains. Type: string extendedAttributeConfiguration Data required by the Registry for some country code top level domains (i.e. example.us). In order to determine if a domain requires extended attributes, use [[SoftLayer_Dns_Domain_Registration::getExtendedAttributes|domain registration]] service.
